teams.name: Super Cool
teams.about: We are a diverse group of badminton lovers. We come from many different countries and a range of ages. Anyone that loves badminton is welcome to join this team! We host have a competitive division and an intermediate division.

teams.name: Pandemonium
teams.about: We are badass badminton players. We are a group of friends that wants to kick some butt on the badminton court!

teams.name: BBC Junior
teams.about: We are the juniors that have trained at Bellevue Badminton Club. We may be young, but we are well trained and will kick your butt!
